<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Eurasian dotterel</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
<div id="contentSub">  (Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Charadrius_morinellus&amp;redirect=no" title="Charadrius morinellus">Charadrius morinellus</a>)</div>
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
